<h1>Download</h1>

Besides the access via this web interface, you can download a copy of the whole database of material properties in a standard json file.

<br/><br/>

The compressed file is only a few MB large and can be download from <a href="/static/db.json.gz" onclick="gtag('event', 'download', {'event_category': 'Files', 'event_label': 'Database'})" download>here</a>.

<br/><br/>

Band structure data is also available for download, but the file is a few GB large, it can be download from <a href="/static/2dmatpedia_band.json.tar.gz" onclick="gtag('event', 'download', {'event_category': 'Files', 'event_label': 'Database'})" download>here</a>.

 
